thread.title: Amy Jones
thread.title_full: Yaniv & Associates, PC reviewed by Amy Jones

author: Amy Jones
title: Amy Jones
text: Efficient, knowledgeable, trust worthy and cost-conscious divorce attorney. I put off getting divorced for many years due to time and expense. Finding Yanniv & Associates changed everything. All of our interactions were professional, concise and pleasant. All emails were responded to quickly. They made the process easy. My divorce was processed in a timely manner. Within three months my divorce was finalized for the cost of $1500. Excellent amazing service.
